CUSTOMER SUPPORT POLICY
Privet!
If you need support relating to Little Orpheus
™
then please email us at
comrades@littleorpheus.com
where we will aim to respond to your enquiry within 48 hours – subject to volume of requests and our opening hours and (09:30 – 17:30 UTC).
Before contacting support channel, you can check our Twitter page
@ChineseRoom
to see if your query has already been answered.
Our support team will be able to help with matters that may be limiting your full enjoyment of the game, for example; crashes, bugs, errors in localisation, inconsistencies with the gameplay or controls.  We are also happy to answer general questions and guide you to relevant documentation where we can.
Unfortunately, we cannot offer support with issues relating to external services such as Game Center or iCloud.
Our customer support is available to all players of Little Orpheus
™
on Apple Arcade when a support request is submitted through our official support channel email:
comrades@littleorpheus.com
although we may address some queries via social media.
